short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides a variety of utilities for JQBX.fm.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: JukeBot provides easy access to some of the most used actions in http://jqbx.fm/. By default, users will be able to view, like, or dislike songs. With room for many more tools, JukeBot also provides special functionality such as automatically liking each song that plays or getting desktop notifications when someone mentions your name in the chat.
